ensure neither party approaches the other directly;

allow [name] to participate in hearings and give evidence:

by live link;

by a recording made [and transcribed at the expense of [the parties equally] / [name(s)]] in advance of the hearing;

with the aid of a [signer] / [insert];

by use of evidence already given in other proceedings, namely [specify];

